&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;You will:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build and drive some of our most critical operational processes&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Own the day-to-day delivery of customer commitments&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Create an effective feedback loop between the front line, product, strategy, and customers&lt;/li&gt;
