&lt;p&gt;Scale’s rapidly growing Global Public Sector team is focused on using AI to address critical challenges facing the public sector around the world. Our core work consists of:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Creating custom AI applications that will impact millions of citizens&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Generating high-quality training data for national LLMs&lt;/li&gt;
