&lt;p&gt;Scale is looking for a Compensation Manager to join our Total Rewards team. In this role, you&#39;ll help build and evolve our global compensation programs by providing analysis, insights, and modeling. We&#39;re seeking someone analytical, fast-paced, and excited about solving hard problems that impact our biggest investment - our people. You&#39;ll play a key role in designing and scaling our compensation processes as we continue to grow.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Responsibilities&lt;/strong&gt;:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Perform quantitative analyses to assist Leadership with key projects&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Conduct market benchmarking to determine pay targets and support business growth&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Contribute to the research, design, and delivery of compensation programs&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support international expansion and M&amp;amp;A initiatives&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with the Recruiting team on offer escalations and process optimization&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop and maintain tools to enhance efficiency of programs&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build and integrate AI into Comp workflows&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Drive clarity, transparency, and understanding of compensation at Scale&lt;/li&gt;
