 benefits such as a commuter stipend.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;title&quot;&gt;The base salary range for this full-time position in the location of Washington DC is:&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;pay-range&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;$203,200&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;divider&quot;&gt;&amp;mdash;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;$254,000 USD&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;content-conclusion&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;PLEASE NOTE:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;Our policy requires a 90-day waiting period before reconsidering candidates for the same role. This allows us to ensure a fair and thorough evaluation of all applicants.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
