&lt;p&gt;The ideal candidate is organized, execution-focused, and thrives on managing complexity. Precision across tracking, documentation, quality alignment, and customer follow-through is what makes customers successful and builds the trust that earns Scale more work. You will be on the front lines of ensuring that these customers become passionate, lifelong Scale partners.&lt;/p&gt;
