&lt;li&gt;Build internal tooling and shared capabilities to accelerate delivery across diverse use cases&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate across engineering, product, and customer teams to streamline execution and reduce friction&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ensure fast, high-quality delivery of features, experiments, and customer launches&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide strategic clarity to your team and attract, hire, and retain world-class engineering talent&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
