&lt;li&gt;Mastery of PyTorch, TensorFlow, JAX, or scikit-learn&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Deep expertise in agentic LLMs and multi-agent systems&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong software engineering and microservices (AWS/GCP)&lt;/li&gt;
