&lt;p class=&quot;p2&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About the Role&lt;br&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;We are seeking a &lt;strong&gt;Principal Architect&lt;/strong&gt; to drive the design, development, and deployment of our agentic AI products in a fast-paced, collaborative, extremely high-visibility environment.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;p2&quot;&gt;In this role, you will lead a team of 50+ engineers, providing both strategic and technical guidance. You’ll be responsible for high-impact architectural decisions, cross-company collaboration, and executive level engagements.&lt;span class=&quot;Apple-converted-space&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;p3&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;Apple-converted-space&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
