&lt;p class=&quot;p2&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Within 6 months:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul class=&quot;ul1&quot;&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;li2&quot;&gt;Successful demonstration of agentic AI’s mission value in high-stakes customer demonstrations&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;li5&quot;&gt;Establish Scale AI as the preferred agentic AI partner for the PEO&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;li5&quot;&gt;Establish high velocity, agile engineering cadence both internally and with our industry partners&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;p2&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Within 12–18 months:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul class=&quot;ul1&quot;&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;li5&quot;&gt;Secure follow-on contract award with expanded scope for Scale&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;li5&quot;&gt;Position Scale AI as the global AI leader in this mission area&lt;/li&gt;
