&lt;p&gt;The &lt;strong&gt;Robotics Operations Manager&lt;/strong&gt; holds primary accountability for the facility’s performance during their assigned shift. Managing an organization of &lt;strong&gt;up to 100 personnel&lt;/strong&gt;, this role ensures the seamless integration of human capital, robotic systems, and data integrity. The Manager is responsible for driving excellence across key operational metrics while fostering a high-performance culture rooted in professional development and continuous process improvement.&lt;/p&gt;
