&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Experience:&lt;/strong&gt; 7+ years of progressive accounting experience, with a mix of Big 4 public accounting and high-growth industry experience (SaaS preferred).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Leadership:&lt;/strong&gt; 3+ years of experience managing and developing high-performing teams.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Technical Rigor:&lt;/strong&gt; Deep expertise in &lt;strong&gt;ASC 606&lt;/strong&gt; and the ability to translate complex technical research into actionable operational policies.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Agility:&lt;/strong&gt; A proven track record of problem-solving in a fast-moving, &quot;ambiguity-heavy&quot; environment.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Systems Fluency:&lt;/strong&gt; Experience with enterprise-level ERPs and revenue recognition software.&lt;/li&gt;
