&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;5+ years&lt;/strong&gt; of full-time software engineering experience (post-graduation).&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong backend engineering fundamentals: &lt;strong&gt;distributed systems&lt;/strong&gt;, &lt;strong&gt;API design&lt;/strong&gt;, data modeling, and production reliability.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong experience with Docker and containerized development/production environments (building images, debugging, and operating container-based services.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
