&lt;p&gt;Scale’s Robotics business unit is currently seeing historic levels of growth. As a &lt;strong&gt;Technical Program Manager (TPM) for Robotics Data&lt;/strong&gt;, you will be the connective tissue across our most complex technical operations, driving initiatives that secure $XXM+ in new revenue.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This isn&#39;t a &quot;sit back and watch&quot; project management role. You will work with multiple project leads across a vast portfolio of robotics data projects, ensuring technical milestones are met, dependencies are de-risked, and stakeholders are aligned. You should be prepared to wear many hats and be excited about intense, impactful work that leads to accelerated career progression.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;You will:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Drive Multi-Project Outcomes:&lt;/strong&gt; Serve as the primary driver for a portfolio of robotics projects, tracking milestones, deliverables, and dependencies to ensure on-time delivery for the world’s leading AI researchers.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Bridge the Technical-Operational Gap:&lt;/strong&gt; Act as the central liaison between AI clients, hardware engineers, and global operational teams to translate high-level goals into executable data collection workflows.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Architect Scalable Pipelines:&lt;/strong&gt; Partner with engineering to design and optimize end-to-end data ingestion pipelines, ensuring they can handle the high-fidelity sensor data (video, logs, teleop) required for Vision-Language-Action (VLA) models.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Enforce Data Quality &amp;amp; Governance:&lt;/strong&gt; Define KPIs and Quality Assurance (QA) metrics to ensure datasets are high-fidelity, labeled correctly, and compliant with rigorous privacy and safety standards.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Standardize for Scale:&lt;/strong&gt; Develop and refine Standard Operating Procedures (SOPs) that allow us to scale collection efforts across global, distributed teams.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Communicate with Precision:&lt;/strong&gt; Provide regular, data-driven progress updates to Scale’s executive team, utilizing SQL and dashboards to monitor performance and guide strategic pivots.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
