&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Strong Technical Foundation:&lt;/strong&gt; A degree in Engineering, Computer Science, or a related field, combined with a deep understanding of AI/ML.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;2-3+ Years of TPM Experience:&lt;/strong&gt; Proven track record of managing complex, cross-functional technical programs, ideally in robotics, hardware, or large-scale data operations.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Hands-on Problem Solving Skills: &lt;/strong&gt;A proactive approach to overcoming technical and logistical roadblocks in a fast-paced environment.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Operational Grit:&lt;/strong&gt; Experience &quot;in the weeds&quot; of operational challenges - you don’t just identify bottlenecks; you build the solution to clear them.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Entrepreneurial Mindset:&lt;/strong&gt; You are comfortable with ambiguity and excited about building infrastructure from scratch in a fast-paced environment.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
