&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Build strong, trust-based relationships with candidates&lt;/strong&gt;, understanding their goals and ensuring an exceptional, personalized journey from first contact to close.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
