&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Design and execute the global travel category strategy&lt;/strong&gt;, leading end-to-end supplier selection (RFP), onboarding, and lifecycle management for airlines, hotels, and ground transportation.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Architect high-leverage negotiation strategies&lt;/strong&gt; to secure preferential rates and corporate benefits, ensuring maximum ROI on the company’s annual travel spend.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Champion &quot;Preferred Supplier&quot; adoption&lt;/strong&gt; through creating policies, data-driven influence and internal marketing, optimizing corporate leverage and volume-based discounts.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Govern the global Travel &amp;amp; Expense (T&amp;amp;E) ecosystem&lt;/strong&gt;, overseeing corporate credit card programs and employee reimbursements to ensure 100% alignment with fiscal policy and tax compliance.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Execute rigorous internal controls and audits&lt;/strong&gt;, identifying leakage or non-compliant spending patterns and implementing corrective action plans.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
